# {{lb|en|adjectival}} [[rushed|Rushed]], [[hurried]]; short of time.
#: {{uxi|fr|I can’t stop now. I'm '''in a hurry'''.}}
# {{lb|en|adverbial}} {{rfdef|en}}

====Usage notes====
* Although it is not comparable, '''hurry''' can be qualified using ''in a '''great''' hurry'', ''in '''more of''' a hurry'', etc.

